{"tid":1249572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係分化 但留？","createTime":"2019-06-21T18:11:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T18:41:22.000Z","uid":37679,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"23bf34337bcddfd04f7dab68b5b8100a2aec4195","tid":1249572,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:11:20.000Z","msg":"不撤不退 唔係講緊唔走<br />\n唔好話咩唔喺在場有資格叫人走定留<br />\n我朝早都出左差唔多10個鐘<br />\n<br />\n如果係想留既 你點叫撤都唔會走架啦<br />\n個個喺度屌哂鬼話做乜叫人走<br />\n消耗戰既結果2014年你未睇過咩<br />\n<br />\n點解唔係留力等聽日後日大後日<br />\n同埋往後既日子先再出黎<br />\n點解要咁糾結留喺度<br />\n你覺得喺度留一既盧偉聰就會走出黎咩<br />\n義士會即刻釋放咩<br />\n<br />\n抗爭冇錯 佔領冇錯 屌警察都冇錯 撚狗冇錯<br />\n但呢場仗 我唔想見到輸在鑽牛角尖 唔理性思考<br />\n<br />\n隔離屌緊鬼屌話做乜唔留既人<br />\n可唔可以話俾我聽你留喺度仲有咩意思"},{"pid":"e71b728206c69f457739a200f69b61a22e540b15","tid":1249572,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:13:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a43bc6983cc4f80c7b63fd73173b6ce25b4cee97","tid":1249572,"uid":254213,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:14:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>垃圾5毛 想出分化post 分化 我地 食屎啦 屌你老母</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4364bc6c2dcdcc6445c7f67d99b7010b2321e905","tid":1249572,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:14:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a548b3a851e83c39e0ec159733d74215a1677b99","tid":1249572,"uid":243691,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:15:23.000Z","msg":"重申一次，屌泛民既人唔係分化撚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1247861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1247861</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9344e2d3c6a6c2c29412ac7c7220e31108761254","tid":1249572,"uid":119667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:16:11.000Z","msg":"真係有人覺得不撤不退等於唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以為一日半日可以解決問題<br />\n聽日後日大後日唔黎?"},{"pid":"bb947cd3431897fcbfb25b75bdbb2a49731aca53